Text: Out of the 4 Soaps..I'm loving DOOL the most right now..I figured out it was Gus about 8 eps ago..it didn't really fit his character though I thought this storyline, he's always been a bit squeamish with how Viv would go, now all of a sudden he's beating women senseless..anyway it's still exciting storylines at moment..Cant wait for Monday's ep..thanks Claudia, be lost without your uploads! :-)
